--------------------------------
TIMER - User Commands

NAME
       timer - the timer of this escape game

SYNOPSIS
       timer

DESCRIPTION
       Print the remaining time until the system restarts.
       
       If the system is corrupted when restarting, you will be trapped
       here forever as the player.

AUTHORS
       Written by Maddy De Wancker, Malak Hayar and Pierre Foulon.

EPO Shell 8.32 - May 2022
